Uhmm you don’t need a username just type in administrator there.
[/quote]Do I Connect To The VPS IP Or The Code They Emailed Me???

You will be emailed the Ip address, it’ll say something like RDC:

IP:
USERNAME:
PASSWORD:

The user name will almost always be Administrator, the password is most likely randomly generated. Check your email.
